features: The ultimate packing partner: Packing cubes set is a new packing tool that is reusable more environmentally friendly, more convenient, wrinkle-free, space-saving and the perfect partner for travel, business, suitcase/luggage and duffel bags. It keeps items organized and viewed. Whether you're a frequent traveler or an occasional adventurer, our packing organizers make packing and unpacking a breeze.

Upgraded Quality: The travel organizers are designed to travel time and time again. Fabric: Use 190D tear-resistant waterproof nylon fabric, which is lighter and stronger. The mesh is LST tested and can with stand 4 times more tension than others. Zipper: use high-quality SBS metal zipper, smooth sliding, two-way zipper, reduce the possibility of jamming. Workmanship: made of damage-resistant high-density stitching construction with hemmed edges all around to avoid fabric stripping.

Multiple sizes cubes: Including 1L (17.71*12.5*4.3cm) for jackets, sweaters, sweatshirts, etc.; 2M (13.8*9.8*4.3cm) for pants, shirts, dresses, etc.; 2S (11.02*6.7*4.3cm) for short sleeves, short skirts, bras, tank tops, etc.; 1XS (13.8*5.12*4.3cm) for underwear, socks, ties and other small items. Traveling with kids can be a challenge, the 4 different sizes of packing cubes make it easy for you to keep everyone's items separate and organized, keeping your family organized.

Visible Breathable Mesh: Each cube has 1 mesh window so you can identify your contents through the mesh to easily find the items you want. In addition, the breathable mesh allows air to circulate, helping to reduce odors and keep clothes fresh and dry.

With confidence - the DEC-MEC suitcase organizer bags set is the perfect travel companion for anyone who wants to stay organized and stress-free on the go. With our versatile, multi-size packing cases and a range of colors and sizes to choose from, you can travel in style and with peace of mind.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Various sizes to accommodate all your items.
reviews.reviewText: Just returned from Italy. Had never used packing cubes before. Now I’m hooked. We moved hotels every 2 days. No drawer space in our 4 star hotels; mostly various shelfs or small wardrobe closet. The cubes keep everything organized and easy to find. Especially loved the long slender one to accommodate bras. I could see thru the netting window the contents without having to guess before unzipping. Love, love, love 💕

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Packing cube set
reviews.reviewText: I got this packing cube set for my daughters first upcoming international trip. If you have never used packing cubes? they are a game changer. It makes it super easy to organize ypur stuff without your luggage exploding all over the room. They are a must habe especially of you are backpacking through multiple cities.This set offers a larger quantity of cubes than other sets I have purchased but tjey are much smaller. This is fine for my purposes but I think it would be harder to use with adult clothes. They do provide a guide on how to compactly fold different articles of clothing which was really nice. This set comes with 6 cubes, a shoe bag, and a small laundry bag.I think for the price it is a good set, just be aware that the cubes are a bit on the smaller end, but if you are backpacking maybe that would be preferable anyway.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Convenient travel aid
reviews.reviewText: I’ve heard a lot about packing cubes, but was not sure these are going to work. They are very lightweight and zipper works with ease. First I tried packing my clothes and clothes in my suitcase without using the cubes, the result was, I couldn’t close my suitcase. So then I decided to give the cubes a try. What’s my clothes are packed into each cube, I placed them into my suitcase. It was almost like magic. They were so compressed everything fit and I zipped up my suitcase no problem at all. These work, so well I think I need another set and switch them out accordingly. This is a great value for the money and they’re easy to clean up just wipe with a damp rag. You can even put them in the washing machine, but on delicate.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent construction and durability
reviews.reviewText: I picked these up to replace the usual plastic grocery bags I use to keep my things organized. One of the big selling points (and very important to me) is the construction quality and stitching. I can confirm that they are made with the care and precision that is claimed. The also come with a tri-fold that illustrates folding and packing tech for various clothing items, which I found informative. For my big items, like shirts and suit coats, I will probably continue to pack them in the same manner as before (stacked together and rolled into a "cinnamon bun" to avoid wrinkles), but for everything else, these are a god-send.Packing bags are pretty generic, and there are many brands to choose from. The build quality, attention to detail, and thoughtful design of Dec-Mec bags sets these apart from the rest. Recommended.
